title: (the number of spots < the number of notes) available to a voice
pid: 39a9f536-9569-4519-bf47-95d0c02589c2
body: |2-
  e.g. sometimes it feels like there are just two likely
  (notes|timbres), sometimes three --
  maybe because there are in fact only that many (when voice = drums),
  or maybe because a pattern is seen repeating across the pitches.
